A link that launches an application isn't recognized as a link in JIRA (despite being proper Markdown). For example, the following link is designed to launch TortoiseSVN with the given repo url.

{noformat}
[Revision 4635](tsvncmd:command:log?path:http://10.1.1.13/svn/SampleDirectory/trunk?rev:4635)
{noformat}

but it results in the following:

[Revision 4635](tsvncmd:command:log?path:http://10.1.1.13/svn/SampleDirectory/trunk?rev:4635)


This code does format correctly on Markdown editor sites such as [http://dillinger.io/]

